import {
    MDBCard,
    MDBCardTitle,
    MDBCardText,
    MDBCardBody,
    MDBCardImage,
    MDBRow,
    MDBCol,
    MDBIcon,
    MDBCardFooter,
} from 'mdb-react-ui-kit';

const Movie = () => {
    return (
        <MDBCard background="dark" className="text-white" alignment="auto-end">
            <MDBRow className="g-0">
                <MDBCol md="4">
                    <MDBCardImage
                        src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tH64gzAHDFg7EFcgfkkZyHdGM5P.jpg"
                        alt="Pôster do filme"
                        fluid
                    />
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol md="8">
                    <MDBCardBody>
                        <MDBCardTitle>Mad Max: Estrada da Fúria</MDBCardTitle>
                        <MDBCardText>
                            Em um mundo apocalíptico, Max Rockatansky...
                        </MDBCardText>
                    </MDBCardBody>
                    <MDBCardFooter border="dark">
                        <MDBCardText className="m-0 g-0">
                            <small className="text-success">
                                <MDBRow>
                                    <MDBCol md="1">
                                        <MDBIcon
                                            fas
                                            icon="dollar-sign"
                                            color="success"
                                            className="me-2"
                                        />
                                    </MDBCol>
                                    <MDBCol>150.000.000</MDBCol>
                                </MDBRow>
                            </small>
                        </MDBCardText>
                        <MDBCardText className="m-0 g-0">
                            <small className="text-success">
                                <MDBRow>
                                    <MDBCol md="1">
                                        <MDBIcon
                                            fas
                                            icon="dollar-sign"
                                            color="success"
                                            className="me-2"
                                        />
                                    </MDBCol>
                                    <MDBCol md="4">378.858.340</MDBCol>
                                </MDBRow>
                            </small>
                        </MDBCardText>
                    </MDBCardFooter>
                </MDBCol>
            </MDBRow>
        </MDBCard>
        /*
        <MDBCard background="dark" className="text-white">
            <MDBCardImage
                src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tH64gzAHDFg7EFcgfkkZyHdGM5P.jpg"
                alt="..."
                position="top"
            />
            <MDBCardBody>
                <MDBCardTitle>Card title</MDBCardTitle>
                <MDBCardText>
                    This is a longer card with supporting text below as a
                    natural lead-in to additional content. This content is a
                    little bit longer.
                </MDBCardText>
            </MDBCardBody>
        </MDBCard>*/
    );
};

export default Movie;
